quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  10,98,"lm yanfae al'iiman 'ahl qaryat amanuu eind meaynt aleadhab 'iilaa 'ahl qaryat yunis bin matta, fa'iinahum lmma ayqnu 'ana aleadhab nazl bihim tabuu 'iilaa allah taealaa tawbatan nswha, flmma tbyan minhum alsidq fi tawbatuhum kashf allah eanhum eadhab alkhizy baed 'an aqtarab mnhm, watarakahum fi aldunya ystmtewn 'iilaa waqt 'iinha' ajalhm"
  10,99,"walaw sha' rabuk -ayha alrswl- al'iiman li'ahl al'ard kuluhum lamnu jmyeana bima jitahum bh, wlkn lah hikmat fi dhlk; fa'iinah yahdi man yasha' wayudilu man yasha' wafq hkmth, walays fi asttaetk 'ana tukrh alnaas ealaa al'iyman"
  10,100,"wma kan linafs 'an tumin biallah 'iilaa bi'iidhnih wtwfyqh, fala tujhd nafsak fi dhlk, fa'iina 'amruhum 'iilaa allh. wayajeal allah aleadhab walkhzy ealaa aladhin la yaeqilun 'amrih wnhyh"
  10,101,"ql -ayha alrswl- lqwmk: tfkru waetbru bima fi alsmwat wal'ard min ayat allah albynat, wlkn alayat walebr walrsl almndhrt eibad allah eqabh, laa tanfae qwmana laa yuminun bishay' min dhlk; l'ieradhm wenadhm"
  10,102,"fhl yantazir hwla' 'iilaa ywmana yeaynwn fih eadhab allah mithl 'ayaam aslafhm almukadhibin aladhin madau qblhm? qul lahum -ayha alrswl-: fantaziruu eiqab allah 'iiniy maeakum min almuntazirin eqabkm"
  10,103,"thm nnjji rusulana waladhin amanuu mehm, wakama najayna 'uwlayik nnjjik -ayha alrswl- waman aman bik tfdla mnna wrhmt"
  10,104,"ql -ayha alrswl- lhwla' alnas: 'iin kuntum fi shakin min sihat diniin aldhy daeawtukum 'ilyh, wahu al'islam wamin thbaty wastqamty elyh, watarjun thwyly enh, fa'iiniy la 'aebud fi hal min al'ahwal ahdana min aladhin tebdwnhm mimaa atakhadhtum min al'asnam walawthan, wlkn 'aebud allah wahdah aldhy yumitukum wyqbd arwahkm, w'umirt 'an 'akun min almsddiqyn bih aleamilin bshreh"
  10,105,"wan 'aqim -ayha alrswl- nafsak ealaa din al'islam mstqymana ealayh ghyr mayl eanh 'iilaa yahudiat wala nsranyt wala eibadat ghyrh, wala takunana mmn yushrik fi eibadat rabih alalihat walandad, fatakun min alhalkyn. whdha wa'iin kan khtabana llrswl salaa allah ealayh wsllam fa'iinah mwjjah lemwm alamt"
  10,106,"wala tade -ayha alrswl- min dun allah shyyana min al'awthan walasnam; li'anaha laa tanfae wala tdrru, fa'iin fealt dhlk wdewtha min dun allah fa'iinak 'idhana min almushrikin ballh, alzaalimin lanfshm balshrk walmesy. whdha wa'iin kan khtabana llrswl salaa allah ealayh wsllam fa'iinah mwjjah lemwm alamt"